<c.white><c.mono_sans>Ah, that alone</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1398
00:40:02.129 --> 00:40:03.450 position:32.86%,start align:start size:44.29% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>You heard the man.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1399
00:40:02.129 --> 00:40:03.450 position:38.57%,start align:start size:30.95% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Get moving.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1400
00:40:03.520 --> 00:40:04.330 position:27.14%,start align:start size:29.05% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Thank you.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1401
00:40:06.839 --> 00:40:07.919 position:38.57%,start align:start size:32.86% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Both of you.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1402
00:40:07.959 --> 00:40:10.079 position:42.38%,start align:start size:36.67% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Yes, yes, yes.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1403
00:40:07.959 --> 00:40:10.079 position:42.38%,start align:start size:48.10% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Go, go, and quickly.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1404
00:40:10.298 --> 00:40:11.528 position:38.57%,start align:start size:51.90% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Keep up the good work.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1405
00:40:29.093 --> 00:40:32.692 position:34.76%,start align:start size:38.57% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Quark, I've got</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1406
00:40:29.093 --> 00:40:32.692 position:34.76%,start align:start size:40.48% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>to say good-bye.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1407
00:40:32.731 --> 00:40:34.032 position:27.14%,start align:start size:50.00% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Oh, just let them go.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1408
00:40:34.371 --> 00:40:35.672 position:19.52%,start align:start size:69.05% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>It'll be less painful that way.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1409
00:40:36.131 --> 00:40:38.552 position:32.86%,start align:start size:57.62% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>No, you don't understand.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1410
00:40:40.150 --> 00:40:41.931 position:23.33%,start align:start size:67.14% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I have to say good-bye to you.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1411
00:40:43.608 --> 00:40:44.448 position:42.38%,start align:start size:48.10% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I'm going with them.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1412
00:40:45.446 --> 00:40:46.312 position:19.52%,start align:start size:44.29% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>But we had a deal.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1413
00:40:47.447 --> 00:40:48.628 position:46.19%,start align:start size:44.29% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I can't stay here.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1414
00:40:49.347 --> 00:40:51.889 position:23.33%,start align:start size:65.24% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Maybe one day I can come back</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1415
00:40:49.347 --> 00:40:51.889 position:23.33%,start align:start size:61.43% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>and we'll be together again</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1416
00:40:51.889 --> 00:40:54.559 position:23.33%,start align:start size:67.14% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>but not until my work is done.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1417
00:40:55.445 --> 00:40:57.246 position:30.95%,start align:start size:48.10% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>So, all I have to do</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1418
00:40:55.445 --> 00:40:57.246 position:34.76%,start align:start size:38.57% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>to get you back</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1419
00:40:57.246 --> 00:41:00.077 position:19.52%,start align:start size:69.05% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>is wait until Cardassia becomes</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1420
00:40:57.246 --> 00:41:00.077 position:19.52%,start align:start size:67.14% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>a free and democratic society?</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1421
00:41:03.804 --> 00:41:06.753 position:57.62%,start align:start size:32.86% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I promise...</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1422
00:41:06.244 --> 00:41:08.323 position:51.90%,start align:start size:32.86% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I'll make it</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1423
00:41:06.244 --> 00:41:08.323 position:51.90%,start align:start size:38.57% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>worth the wait.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1424
00:41:20.279 --> 00:41:24.078 position:29.05%,start align:start size:51.90% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I could come with you.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1425
00:41:20.279 --> 00:41:24.078 position:34.76%,start align:start size:38.57% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I don't suppose</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1426
00:41:24.156 --> 00:41:26.958 position:27.14%,start align:start size:55.71% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>No, it's not your fight.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1427
00:41:27.835 --> 00:41:29.914 position:29.05%,start align:start size:51.90% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Besides, I could never</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1428
00:41:27.835 --> 00:41:29.914 position:34.76%,start align:start size:40.48% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>live with myself</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1429
00:41:29.914 --> 00:41:31.159 position:25.24%,start align:start size:65.24% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>if something happened to you.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1430
00:41:32.186 --> 00:41:34.615 position:44.29%,start align:start size:46.19% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I need to know that</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1431
00:41:32.186 --> 00:41:34.615 position:44.29%,start align:start size:44.29% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>you're here, safe.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1432
00:41:35.456 --> 00:41:37.975 position:30.95%,start align:start size:51.90% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>That way, a part of</c.mono_sans></c.white><c.white><c.mono_sans><i> me</i></c.mono_sans></c.white>

1433
00:41:35.456 --> 00:41:37.975 position:30.95%,start align:start size:57.62% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>will always be safe, too.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1434
00:41:47.812 --> 00:41:49.411 position:46.19%,start align:start size:44.29% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I love you, Quark.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1435
00:41:51.091 --> 00:41:52.611 position:42.38%,start align:start size:36.67% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I always will.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1436
00:42:07.926 --> 00:42:09.405 position:34.76%,start align:start size:40.48% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I love you, too.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1437
00:42:13.102 --> 00:42:15.824 position:19.52%,start align:start size:46.19% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I suggest we return</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1438
00:42:13.102 --> 00:42:15.824 position:19.52%,start align:start size:69.05% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>to the Promenade without delay.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1439
00:42:17.981 --> 00:42:21.447 position:42.38%,start align:start size:48.10% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>You have to tell me.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1440
00:42:17.981 --> 00:42:21.447 position:42.38%,start align:start size:44.29% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Why did you do it?</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1441
00:42:20.779 --> 00:42:21.899 position:57.62%,start align:start size:32.86% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Shoot Toran.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1442
00:42:21.940 --> 00:42:24.298 position:19.52%,start align:start size:50.00% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Well, why did you let</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1443
00:42:21.940 --> 00:42:24.298 position:19.52%,start align:start size:44.29% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Professor Lang go?</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1444
00:42:24.338 --> 00:42:26.777 position:48.10%,start align:start size:42.38% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I have no choice.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1445
00:42:24.338 --> 00:42:26.777 position:48.10%,start align:start size:30.95% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I love her.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1446
00:42:26.777 --> 00:42:28.657 position:19.52%,start align:start size:50.00% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>And I love Cardassia,</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1447
00:42:28.736 --> 00:42:30.897 position:19.52%,start align:start size:32.86% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>which is why</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1448
00:42:28.736 --> 00:42:30.897 position:19.52%,start align:start size:53.81% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I had to do what I did.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1449
00:42:33.136 --> 00:42:34.257 position:44.29%,start align:start size:46.19% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I don't understand.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1450
00:42:36.003 --> 00:42:38.396 position:19.52%,start align:start size:63.33% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>That's the thing about love.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1451
00:42:38.396 --> 00:42:39.836 position:19.52%,start align:start size:34.76% line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>No one really</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1452
00:42:38.396 --> 00:42:39.836 position:19.52%,start align:start size:55.71% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>understands it, do they?</c.mono_sans></c.white>

